{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"a5364bccfb","title":"给王均”的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"09aa37f806","index":0,"year":1936,"month":9,"day":8,"articleId":"a5364bccfb"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji9-1","name":"毛泽东全集第9卷(1)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji9-1.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji9-1":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"9177ef8b53","type":"paragraph","text":"给王均”的信","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"a5364bccfb"},{"id":"3538dcd6fa","type":"paragraph","text":"（1936年9月8日）治平先生：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"a5364bccfb"},{"id":"9b71954d97","type":"paragraph","text":"从井冈山就同先生打起，打了十年，也可以休息了！我们致国民党书，为了共同抗日，实全国一致之要求，先生爱国健儿，对此谅有同感！朱玉阶同志极愿与先生合作，如能与之互通声气，自己元气少消耗一分，则抗日力量多保存一分。两党合作之局既为时不远，双方前线宜尽可能减少冲突。如何之处，敬候卓裁。顺颂勋祺。不一。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"a5364bccfb"},{"id":"bb1c4857a8","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"a5364bccfb"},{"id":"817d43ef08","type":"paragraph","text":"九月八日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"a5364bccfb"},{"id":"ec4207fe61","type":"paragraph","text":"[1]王均（1891—1936），字治平，云南呈贡人，当时任国民党军第三军军长。","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"a5364bccfb"},{"id":"c2042b6920","type":"paragraph","text":"[2]朱玉阶，即朱德。他和王均曾在云南陆军讲武堂同学。","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"a5364bccfb"}],"page":{"id":"3fd92ea826","publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"a5364bccfb","start":114,"end":114}}}},"__N_SSG":true}